  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:85px 1fr 1fr 1fr;margin-top:0.7rem;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:0.6rem;text-align:center;color:#7a8499;">
    <div></div>
    <div>|ψ₀⟩</div>
    <div>|ψ₁⟩ after CNOT+H</div>
    <div>|ψ₂⟩ after correction</div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:0.8rem;font-size:0.72rem;color:#7a8499;font-style:italic;">
    Classical communication (x, y) from Alice to Bob shown as dashed lines. Bob's correction uses at most two gates.
