    <div class="feedback hint" id="h9a">α ∈ ℝ gives 1 parameter. β = β_R + jβ_I gives 2 more. Normalisation α²+β_R²+β_I²=1 is already used to set the scale — it doesn't reduce the count further. Total: 3.</div>
    <div class="feedback" id="f9a"></div>
