</div>

<div class="ex-block" id="ex9b">
  <div class="ex-header"><span class="ex-tag">Ex 9.2</span><span class="ex-title">Estimating α</span></div>
  <div class="ex-body">
    <p>In N=1000 Z-basis measurements we observe N₀ = 640 outcomes of "0". What is the estimate for α? (give 2 decimal places, e.g. 0.80)</p>
  </div>
  <div class="answer-area">
