  </div>
</div>

<div class="ex-block" id="ex9c">
  <div class="ex-header"><span class="ex-tag">Ex 9.3</span><span class="ex-title">Estimating β_R</span></div>
  <div class="ex-body">
    <p>Using α = 0.80 from Ex 9.2, in N=1000 X-basis measurements we observe N₀ = 620. What is the estimate for β_R? (give 2 decimal places)</p>
  </div>
  <div class="answer-area">
    <div class="answer-row">
      <span class="ans-label">β_R ≈</span>
      <input class="answer-input" id="a9c" placeholder="0.??" oninput="chkClose('a9c', 0.15, 0.02, 'ex9c')" style="width:100px;">
      <button class="btn sm" onclick="chkClose('a9c', 0.15, 0.02, 'ex9c')">Check</button>
      <button class="hint-toggle" onclick="showHint('h9c')">show hint</button>
    </div>
    <div class="feedback hint" id="h9c">β_R = (2·N₀/N − 1)/(2α) = (2·0.620 − 1)/(2·0.80) = (1.24−1)/1.60 = 0.24/1.60 = 0.15.</div>
    <div class="feedback" id="f9c"></div>
